<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/426403-is-there-a-prequel-to-this-the-main">Is there a prequel to this? The main character, &quot;Consul&quot; has no real history but the narrator keeps referring to incidents in his past. In addition, the planet is described as if we have been there before.</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_426403'><a id="like_count_community_question_426403" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/426403?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">3 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F77566.Hyperion">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/426403-is-there-a-prequel-to-this-the-main">6 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/426403-is-there-a-prequel-to-this-the-main">See all 8 answers</a>
</li>
</ul>
</div>

